        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nThis is one of 3 coordinated commits.\n\n\nThis robot health-check change was blessed by Brian:\n\n```\nIttay,\n\nWe found the problem in SO and were able to successfully use robot via HTTPS/8443 to VID for instantiateVFWCL and Health check.\n\nintegration_robot_properties.py:#GLOBAL_VID_SERVER_PROTOCOL = 'http'\nintegration_robot_properties.py:#GLOBAL_VID_SERVER_PORT = '8080'\nintegration_robot_properties.py:GLOBAL_VID_SERVER_PROTOCOL = 'https'\nintegration_robot_properties.py:GLOBAL_VID_SERVER_PORT = '8443'\n\nSo we can make a coordinated change in testsuite and VID whenever you are ready.\n\nBrian\n```",
